NK035(ci)002:0: man ngag nges pa'i kha byang ming rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK035(ci)002:2: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK035(ci)002:3: sku gsum nyid ni snang ba 'di nyid las //
NK035(ci)002:4: ma nor dbang po'i yul du gtan dbab phyir //
NK035(ci)002:5: man ngag yid chung gsal ba snying nor grags //
NK035(ci)002:6: me long nyid la bzhin bstan ji bzhin du //
NK035(ci)002:7: ma nor 'gyur ba'i sa med gsang chen nyid //
NK035(ci)002:8: snyigs ma'i dus su gang zag la la dag /
NK035(ci)002:9: snying po'i nor la ras chod gzu lum gyis //
NK035(ci)002:10: brtsams shing mun pa'i nang du khab gtor ltar //
NK035(ci)002:11: man ngag snying po dkrugs shing lhag chad byed /
NK035(ci)002:12: de rnams kyis ni bsnan phri byar med phyir //
NK035(ci)002:13: ming nges gsang ba'i kha byang 'di nyid ni //
NK035(ci)002:14: dam pa rnams la lus ngag yid kyis kyang //
NK035(ci)002:15: rab tu gus pas gsol ba btab nas kyang //
NK035(ci)002:16: ma 'ongs snyigs ma'i dus su dgos srid pas //
NK035(ci)002:17: 'khrul pa med pa'i blo yis 'bri bar bya //
NK035(ci)002:18: gsang ba'i man ngag yi ge 'di nyid ni //
NK035(ci)002:19: gcig la gcig dgos ma bu ma yin te /
NK035(ci)002:20: gnad kyi man ngag nges pa so so'i thabs //
NK035(ci)002:21: nges pa'i snying po man ngag nges pa'i grangs //
NK035(ci)002:22: bla med yongs su rdzogs pa'i sde tshan la //
NK035(ci)002:23: 'di dag yi ge gsang ba'i gnad du phab //
NK035(ci)002:24: 'di ltar mig gi kha byang nges pa la //
NK035(ci)002:25: gsang ba'i man ngag kha byang yi ge ni //
NK035(ci)002:26: nges par grangs su bcad na 'di ltar mchis //
NK035(ci)002:27: rgya cher bshad pa'i yi ge grangs mang yang //
NK035(ci)002:28: rnam par bsdus na snying po'i don nyid ni //
NK035(ci)002:29: brgya dang bcu dgu nyid du bkod pa la //
NK035(ci)002:30: re res kyang ni grol ba'i snying po'o //
NK035(ci)002:31: lta ba'i skor bzhi'i rtsa nges dum dum khrigs 1su ltos //
NK035(ci)002:32: ston pa'i lo rgyus la sogs po ti smug chung 2ltos //
NK035(ci)002:33: 'khul zhig gsal ba'i me long 3nyid dang 'byung bzhi gnad yig 4dang //
NK035(ci)002:34: rin chen gser 5thig nyid dang snang byed sgron ma 6dang //
NK035(ci)002:35: 'od gsal lde mig 7nyid dang shes bya skor gsum 8dang //
NK035(ci)002:36: gsang ba'i sdom 9byang nyid dang sgra brtags 'khor 10lo nyid //
NK035(ci)002:37: sku gsum lag 11khrid dang ni mkha' 'gro pra khrid 12dang //
NK035(ci)002:38: babs lugs gsum 13skor dang ni 'khrul pa'i sdom yig 14gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:39: gsang thig 15chen po dang ni gser 1 6byang bkol ba nyid //
NK035(ci)002:40: lam khrigs chen po 17dang ni ye shes lag phrad 18gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:41: bka' khrol chen po 19dang ni bsam gtan rang 20gnas gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:42: gsal ba'i me long 21nyid dang gsang ba nyid bkol 22gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:43: snang ba bsdus 23pa dang ni gnas pa'i byung khungs 24gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:44: khregs chod bdun 25pa dang ni thod rgal dgu pa 26gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:45: lung bstan chen mo 27dang ni glang chen drug pa 28gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:46: spyod lam bsdus 29pa dang ni lta ba'i gser 30bkod gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:47: pad+ma'i klong yangs 31dang ni lha yi phyag 32sor ma //
NK035(ci)002:48: gser gyi ut+pala 33nyid dang dran pa rgyud gcod 34gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:49: rags pa 35nyams blangs nyid dang phra rgyun dril 36ba gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:50: gsal ba'i sgron ma 37nyid dang seng 38ge rtsal sprug gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:51: a ti rnal dgongs 39dang ni dgos don bzhi pa 40pa gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:52: rdo rje lam 41bstan dang ni rin chen 'od 'bar 42nyid //
NK035(ci)002:53: lhag pa'i 'khor 43lo dang ni khyung chen mkha' 44lding gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:54: lta ba'i mig sel 45nyid dang bla ma'i rim 46pa gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:55: drang ba'i tshig 47rgyud dang ni 'khrul gzhi rtsad chod 48gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:56: sems kyi dmigs drug nyid 49dang sgom pa'i 'khor lo 50gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:57: dbang gi lde 51mig nyid dang dbang gi las byang 52gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:58: spros med dbang gi man ngag 53dag dang dbang gi rtsa 54ba gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:59: dbang gi rigs 'byed 55nyid dang dbang gi phra tig gnyis56 //
NK035(ci)002:60: 'khor lo drug pa'i 57dbang dang dam tshig rab 58'byed gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:61: dbang bkod chen po 59nyid dang dbang sbyor pra khrid 60gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:62: rig pa'i me tog 61nyid dang gser 62lung chen po dang //
NK035(ci)002:63: man ngag rtsa 63ba nyid dang lung tig bco 64brgyad pa //
NK035(ci)002:64: rig pa drug 65pa dang ni sems lung sgom khrigs 66gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:65: yang gsang 67dril ba dang ni spas pa'i nyi ma 68dang //
NK035(ci)002:66: 'phra bkod bcu 69pa dang ni lung yig 70bsdus pa gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:67: bdud rtsi 71yang zhun dang ni lug gsum 72'dus pa nyid //
NK035(ci)002:68: gsang chen g.yu yig 73can dang man ngag phra yig 74can //
NK035(ci)002:69: gsang ba gser 75yig can dang snying gzer 76che chung dang //
NK035(ci)002:70: bsam gtan nyal ba'i 'khor 77lo dang ni 'phrul yig 78che chung dang //
NK035(ci)002:72: gsang ba'i gzer 81bu dang ni rtsa gnas 'khor 82lo dag /
NK035(ci)002:73: bsam gtan babs 83lung dang ni rig 84pas 'byed gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:74: snang ba rgyas 85'debs nyid dang ye shes sbubs 'jug 86gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:75: lo rgyus chen 87mo nyid dang gsal ba'i zhal 88chems nyid //
NK035(ci)002:76: theg pa'i bsdus 89shan dang ni gsang ba'i sgra yig 90gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:77: yi ge'i sgra bshad 91dang ni sgra bzhi mtshams 92sbyor gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:78: bstan pa'i go 93cha ma dang 'gyur med thig le 94gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:79: dang po'i 95kha bsgyur dang ni 'bras bu 96mngon byed gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:80: stong pa'i mtha' 97'byed dang ni nam mkha' lam 98khyer gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:81: thi bya tshang 'jug 99dang ni gsal ba rin chen 'od100 //
NK035(ci)002:82: ka dag chen po'i dag yig 101yig dang ni lhun grub yi ge 102gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:83: shes rab 'khor lo 103dang ni smra ba'i mtshon 104chen gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:84: ye shes lnga bskor 105dang ni 'od kyi tshul 106bshad gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:85: 'byung ba'i gnas 107'byed dang ni sgron ma'i khungs 108gcod gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:86: phyag rgyas 109dus pa dang ni bkod pa 110lnga pa gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:87: rgya mtsho ar 111gtad dang ni rlung ni sdom byang 112gnyis //
NK035(ci)002:88: ngo sprod gsum 113pa dang ni babs lugs 114bcu gcig pa //
NK035(ci)002:89: rtsa thig 115che chung dang ni rlung gi stems 116yig dang //
NK035(ci)002:90: rigs pa'i gnas 117sa dang ni mig gi bsam 118gtan no //
NK035(ci)002:91: de ltar man ngag yig chung brgya dang bcu dgu ni //
NK035(ci)002:92: gcig la gcig brten ma yin 'gal med so so'i gnad //
NK035(ci)002:93: nges par gang zag re la phan pa dang //
NK035(ci)002:94: dgos pa'i yig chung rgyud la phan pa dang //
NK035(ci)002:95: snying po rab tu bsdus pa nyi tshe las //
NK035(ci)002:96: gnad med yi ge gcig kyang ma mchis so //
NK035(ci)002:97: gsang chen dam pa'i yi ge 'di dag ni //
NK035(ci)002:98: mthar thug man ngag nges pa'i gnad yin pas //
NK035(ci)002:99: skal ldan sems kyi bu yis yid la chongs //
NK035(ci)002:100: sku gsum ye shes lnga nyid sa la goms pa yi //
NK035(ci)002:101: thabs kyi yan lag rnams su 'di dag 'gro //
NK035(ci)002:102: lhag pa'i yi ge gsang ba'i gnad 'di yis //
NK035(ci)002:103: gang gi dug gsum nad rnams 'don par byed pa'o //
NK035(ci)002:104: gsang ba'i man ngag yig chung nges pa'i grangs //
NK035(ci)002:105: snyigs ma'i dus su 'di nyid dgos srid pas //
NK035(ci)002:106: ma 'ongs skal ldan 'di la 'jug pa rnams //
NK035(ci)002:107: snying po don gyi yi ge'i grangs nyid las //
NK035(ci)002:108: the tshom blo yis spros pa gcod pa'i phyir //
NK035(ci)002:109: ma nor dmigs bstan man ngag nges pa'i grangs //
NK035(ci)002:110: the tshom bsal phyir man ngag nges pa yi //
NK035(ci)002:111: ming rnams nges pa'i kha byang 'di bris pas //
NK035(ci)002:112: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don 'di la //
NK035(ci)002:113: mos 'jug dad pa'i skal ba ldan pa la //
NK035(ci)002:114: mun pa'i nang du sgron me btegs pa ltar //
NK035(ci)002:115: ji ltar snang ba'i 'od kyis chos rnams kun //
NK035(ci)002:116: rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid du shes par shog /
NK035(ci)002:117: man ngag nges pa'i kha byang ming rnam par bkod pa /
NK035(ci)002:118: slob dpon chen po byi ma la mu tras mdzad pa rdzogs so ////
